description.en:
GBANK APY is a decentralized crypto asset which rewards holders with a fixed compound interest through the use of it's unique Auto staking & Auto-compounding mechanism. 
$GBANK APY  is a Bep20 token, Symbol (GBK) which rewards its holders with automatic passive interest payments every 3 Seconds.
Our entire protocol's smart contract was written and developed from scratch from our own competent group of developers. GBANK APY (GBK) works on a completely new set of mechanics which allows for complete protocol sustainability.
GbankAPY's tokenomics is also completely unique as our Auto-Burn mechanism aids the healthy upward progression of GBANK APY floor price.
